---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
const contactEmail = "hello@readystackdigital.com";
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy & Cookie Policy | ReadyStack Digital"
  description="How ReadyStack Digital handles your information, including our AI assistant, cookies and browser storage, subprocessors, data retention and your privacy rights."
  path="/privacy"
  heading="Privacy & Cookie Policy"
  updated="30 May 2026"
>
  <p class="legal-lead">
    ReadyStack Digital ("we", "us", "our") builds and manages websites and digital
    services for businesses across Australia. This policy explains what information we
    collect, how we use it, who helps us process it, and your rights. We handle personal
    information in line with the Australian Privacy Act 1988 and the Australian Privacy
    Principles (APPs).
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Enquiries you send us</strong>: when you use our contact form, chat
      assistant or message us on WhatsApp, we collect the details you provide (such as
      your name, email, phone number and what you're interested in).</li>
    <li><strong>Conversation content</strong>: the messages (and voice notes, if you
      send them) you exchange with our AI assistant.</li>
    <li><strong>Basic technical information</strong>: such as your IP address and, on
      the website, the page an enquiry was started from. We use this for delivery,
      security and abuse prevention.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We do <strong>not</strong> ask for or store payment card details, banking
    information, government identifiers or other sensitive information. Please don't
    share these with us through the website or chat.
  </p>

  <h2>Our AI assistant ("Stack")</h2>
  <p>
    We offer an AI assistant called <strong>Stack</strong> on our website and via
    WhatsApp. Stack answers questions about our services, provides indicative ("from")
    pricing, captures enquiries and helps you book a call.
    <strong>Stack is an automated AI assistant, not a human.</strong> You're told this up
    front, and you can reach a real person at any time by typing <strong>"human"</strong>, and we'll have our team follow up. Conversations are processed to generate replies and
    may be reviewed to improve the service and investigate misuse.
  </p>

  <h2>How we use your information</h2>
  <p>
    To answer your questions, generate AI replies, capture and follow up on enquiries,
    book calls, send you the information you ask for, keep the service secure and prevent
    abuse, and to review and improve our website and assistant.
  </p>

  <h2>Who processes your data (subprocessors)</h2>
  <p>To run our website and assistant we share the minimum necessary data with:</p>
  <div class="legal-table-wrap">
    <table class="legal-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Provider</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Google (Gemini)</td><td>Generates the AI assistant's replies</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Cloudflare</td><td>Hosting, database, AI fallback model and bot protection</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Meta Platforms (WhatsApp)</td><td>Delivers and receives WhatsApp messages</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Cal.com</td><td>Discovery-call booking</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Resend</td><td>Sends enquiry notification emails to our team</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Web3Forms</td><td>Delivers website contact-form submissions to us</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2>Overseas processing</h2>
  <p>
    Some of these providers process data on servers <strong>outside Australia</strong>
    (for example, in the United States). By using our website and assistant you
    acknowledge that your information may be processed overseas, consistent with
    Australian Privacy Principle 8.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies &amp; browser storage</h2>
  <p>
    Our website does not use advertising or cross-site tracking cookies. Our chat widget
    stores a single <strong>session identifier</strong> in your browser's
    <strong>local storage</strong> (key: <code>rs_session_id</code>) so your conversation
    stays connected as you navigate or return later. This is not shared with third
    parties. If we detect suspicious activity, the widget may load
    <strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong>, an invisible bot-protection check that only
    confirms you're human and does not track you across websites. You can clear this any
    time by clearing your browser's site data for readystackdigital.com.
  </p>

  <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Conversation transcripts:</strong> retained for <strong>30 days</strong>, then deleted.</li>
    <li><strong>Abuse and security logs:</strong> retained for <strong>90 days</strong>, then deleted.</li>
    <li><strong>Enquiry details</strong> you provide are kept for as long as needed to respond to and manage your enquiry.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    You can stop using the assistant at any time. Under the Australian Privacy Act 1988
    you may request <strong>access to, correction of, or deletion of</strong> your
    personal information, and you may make a privacy complaint. Contact us at
    <a href={"mailto:" + contactEmail}>{contactEmail}</a>. If you're not satisfied with
    our response, you can contact the Office of the Australian Information Commissioner
    (OAIC) at <a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener">oaic.gov.au</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>WhatsApp</h2>
  <p>
    If you message us on WhatsApp, your messages are also handled by WhatsApp/Meta under
    their own terms and privacy policy. We can only reply within WhatsApp's standard
    24-hour customer-service window after your most recent message.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this policy or your information? Email
    <a href={"mailto:" + contactEmail}>{contactEmail}</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
